What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I'd absolutely recommend something like this to a fellow student. I would jump at the opportunity to work with Crowley again.

This was an independent study -- so it will obviously vary by professor and project. Still, I highly recommend doing this. IF you're a writing concentrator, do it another semester! If you're not, do it as a kind of sneaky way into having a writing concentration senior project.
If you love poetry, you shouldn't leave Yale without trying this.
